quran[8{c,v,t}:
29,7,aur jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay hum un ke gunaaho ko unn se daur kar dein ge aur un ko un ke aamaal ka bohat acha badla den ge
29,8,aur hum ne ensaan ko apne maa baap ke sath naik sulooq karne ka hukum diya hai. ( ae mukhatib ) agar tairay maa baap tairay darpay hon ke to mere sath kisi ko shareek banaye jis ki haqeeqat ki tujhe waqfiyat nahi. to un ka kehna nah mannio. tum ( sab ) ko meri taraf lout kar aana hai. phir jo kuch tum karte they mein tum ko jta dun ga
29,9,aur jo log imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay un ko hum naik logon mein daakhil karen ge
29,10,aur baaz log aisay hain jo kehte hain ke hum khuda par imaan laaye jab unn ko khuda ( ke raste ) mein koi aeza pahunchti hai to logon ki aeza ko ( yun ) samajte hain jaisay khuda ka azaab. agar tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se madad puhanche to kehte hain ke hum tumahray sath they.kiya jo ahal aalam ke seenon mein hai khuda is se waaqif nahi ?
29,11,aur khuda unn ko zaroor maloom kere ga jo ( sachey ) momin hain aur mnafqon ko bhi maloom karkay rahay ga
29,12,aur jo kafir hain woh mominoun se kehte hain ke hamaray tareeq ki pairwi karo hum tumahray gunah athaliN ge. halaank woh unn ke gunaaho ka kuch bhi boojh aُthane walay nahi. kuch shak nahi ke yeh jhutay hain
29,13,aur yeh apne boojh bhi uthain ge aur apne bojhon ke sath aur ( logon ke ) boojh bhi. aur jo bohtan yeh bandhte rahay qayamat ke din unn ki unn se zaroor prssh hogi
29,14,aur hum ne Nooh ko unn ki qoum ki taraf bheja to woh un mein pachaas baras kam hazaar baras rahay phir unn ko tufaan ( ke azaab ) ne aapkrha. aur woh zalim they
